                     <incipit type="preface">In Christo sibi dilecto quondam conscolari &amp; confratri moderno</incipit>
                     <incipit type="type">De triplici abstinencia. Cap. 1. Abstinencie triplex est species</incipit>
                     <note>In 87 chapters, consisting of an alphabetical series of discourses on theological and moral subjects, illustrated by quotations and by 'narraciones', some dated, 1310 (fol. 39v) 1247 (fol. 43v), 1298 (fol. 71), 1265 (fol. 104v), 1356 (fol. 134). A list of chapters is at fol. ii.</note>
                     <note>On fol. 173 is a 16th cent. reference to a 'Scala Perfectionis' by Walter Hilton. The lower margins of fols. 62, 65 are cut off.</note>
